        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>National ACERT Grant Program Authorization Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Justice, in coordination with the Department of Health and Human Services, to award grants for states, tribal nations, localities, and community-based organizations to establish response teams to address adverse childhood experiences associated with exposure to trauma.</p>]]>
